{"type":"message","id":"677dc825","parentId":"fc6dfdd9","timestamp":"2026-03-20T12:19:30.977Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-03-20 20:19 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 讨论话题：收集新闻、整理新闻，应该由谁来负责？是中书省、尚书省，还是其他部门？请给出你的观点和理由。回复格式：部门 + 理由，简洁有力。"}],"timestamp":1774009170975}}
{"type":"message","id":"f2650b1e","parentId":"677dc825","timestamp":"2026-03-20T12:19:36.758Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The subagent task is asking me to discuss who should be responsible for collecting and organizing news - whether it should be the 中书省 (Chancellery), 尚书省 (Secretariat), or another department. This is a historical/institutional discussion about ancient Chinese government structures.\n\nLet me give my view directly as a subagent response.","thinkingSignature":"fc150d5b98ce6c4c0bcbe094a7697f5707eb17838054b26b452fe6068ac44d6f"},{"type":"text","text":"**尚书省**。\n\n理由：尚书省是最高行政机关，负责执行落地，新闻收集整理本质是信息处理与分发的事务性工作，归尚书省最为合适——中书省掌诏令决策，门下省掌审议封驳，皆非执行机构。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":120,"output":126,"cacheRead":21201,"cacheWrite":12892,"totalTokens":34339,"cost":{"input":0.000048,"output":0.000189,"cacheRead":0.00084804,"cacheWrite":0.0019337999999999998,"total":0.00301884}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774009170977}}
